statement: (select tbla.s_nation, tbla.d_year, tblb.s_suppkey, tblb.s_region || "hello" as s_region from (select * from v_ssb where profit is not null) tbla left join (select * from supplier where s_suppkey > 100) tblb on tbla.s_nation = tblb.s_nation where length(tblb.s_phone) > 5 and s_city is not null) minus select * from from_temp_3;
